" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"720\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image shows an orc and human from Warcraft 2. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image shows an orc and human from Warcraft 2. \" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/36a921a64d7372dad3b22e6f1dd24d85.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/36a921a64d7372dad3b22e6f1dd24d85.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/36a921a64d7372dad3b22e6f1dd24d85.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image shows an orc and human from Warcraft 2. \" data-chomp-id=\"36a921a64d7372dad3b22e6f1dd24d85\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"720\" data-alt=\"An image shows an orc and human from Warcraft 2. \" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/36a921a64d7372dad3b22e6f1dd24d85.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Blizzard\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"36a921a64d7372dad3b22e6f1dd24d85\" data-recommend-id=\"image://36a921a64d7372dad3b22e6f1dd24d85\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"720\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image shows an orc and human from Warcraft 2. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBlizzard has announced that the original \u003cem\u003eWarcraft\u003c/em\u003e and \u003cem\u003eWarcraft 2\u003c/em\u003e, as well as its expansions, are being remastered and re-released as part of a new Battle Chest. This new package also includes \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/games/warcraft-iii-reign-of-chaos\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/warcraft-iii-reign-of-chaos\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eWarcraft 3 Reforged\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, which has received a new update improving its visuals. And all of this is available today.  - Zack Zwiezen \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/warcraft-2-3-rts-classic-remastered-blizzard-pc-1851697730\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/warcraft-2-3-rts-classic-remastered-blizzard-pc-1851697730\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426\" data-recommend-id=\"image://d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"GOG\u0026#39;s logo for preserved games, on a background of game covers.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"GOG\u0026#39;s logo for preserved games, on a background of game covers.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"GOG\u0026#39;s logo for preserved games, on a background of game covers.\" data-chomp-id=\"d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"GOG\u0026#39;s logo for preserved games, on a background of game covers.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: GOG\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426\" data-recommend-id=\"image://d68f6ab250452357716182523dae3426\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"GOG\u0026#39;s logo for preserved games, on a background of game covers.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn 2008, when \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;External link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://www.gog.com/\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://www.gog.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eGOG.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e was launched, it was called Good Old Games. As Steam was on the rise and digital distribution was clearly to become the future of gaming, a Polish company that had just released its first game—a relatively obscure RPG called \u003cem\u003eThe Witcher\u003c/em\u003e—wanted to get in on the act. The goal was updating and preserving classic gaming, and selling it without any form of DRM. Over the years, GOG seemed to drift away from this origin, and shift its focus to trying to compete as a distribution platform for AAA gaming, going head-to-head with Valve’s behemoth. But today marks a big change. - John Walker \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/gog-games-preservation-program-drm-1851696363\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/gog-games-preservation-program-drm-1851696363\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"448291c8c64307337f81b8c914668202\" data-recommend-id=\"image://448291c8c64307337f81b8c914668202\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A head crab zombies shambles toward the player.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A head crab zombies shambles toward the player.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/448291c8c64307337f81b8c914668202.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/448291c8c64307337f81b8c914668202.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/448291c8c64307337f81b8c914668202.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A head crab zombies shambles toward the player.\" data-chomp-id=\"448291c8c64307337f81b8c914668202\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"A head crab zombies shambles toward the player.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"http